大得黎好自卑，<br />\n我有次傾計夾左Schedule呢個字落去，<br />\n佢問完我呢個字咩意思之後，<br />\n再問我一句: 咁點解唔講行程表要講「屎架吱噢」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb0b8e5a323974dca7b5b333bc9b79bf7e45ab0","tid":252170,"uid":45138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:14:35.000Z","msg":"台狗笑鳩香港係大陸喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明兩面都講緊狗話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ae79ab9c37c0ac6d8fd86f857385230dc6ed1f","tid":252170,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:18:36.000Z","msg":"nice<br />\n奶子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bde851c25323b0f69737af5a3d2871dca2146e","tid":252170,"uid":77697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:38:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台狗笑鳩香港係大陸喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明兩面都講緊狗話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地係咁架啦，自以為是，好多台狗都未出過城成日以為台北就係世界中心。但其實台北只係一個三等城市，我舊同學嫁左過去台北佢話好似去左廣州咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69dc1e54cdaf051026543bafd41b3b270ea789d9","tid":252170,"uid":77697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:38:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>nice<br />\n奶子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nnice，瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf9f38f18ba7d76b1e9f081d3dc065ba8531c89","tid":252170,"uid":48242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:40:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0660796893cd9efe1eca092954a6a4fcf06dac9","tid":252170,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:44:10.000Z","msg":"連登好多五毛搞分化，明明全世界個講英文都有口音，呢個係英文在地化嘅正常現象，好似日本咁。<br />\n<br />\n同埋要笑都笑咗支那先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45e06885f377dc4910489161ed1f7f0611ddb0d","tid":252170,"uid":36510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:51:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>台狗笑鳩香港係大陸喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明兩面都講緊狗話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地係咁架啦，自以為是，好多台狗都未出過城成日以為台北就係世界中心。但其實台北只係一個三等城市，我舊同學嫁左過去台北佢話好似去左廣州咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要睇咩台狗,<br />\n本身係由其他縣市去台北嘅都正常少少,<br />\n屌佢老母有班台北on9以成世未出過台北為榮,<br />\n仲要話台灣其他地區嘅人係鄉下仔,<br />\n真係on9到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22afba60238e91afb60b23750d52105a7d289cec","tid":252170,"uid":36510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:53:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我唔係正音撚<br />\n但講真個&quot;g&quot;字真係咁難發咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣同大陸喱都咁讀<br />\n果然係一家親</blockquote><br />\n戀愛IN <span style=\"color: red;\">豬</span><br />\n永遠g當豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm